724815f.title: Manhattan: Wooster Street - Broome Street
724815f.text:
76, 80-82 Wooster Street, east side, between Broome and Spring
Streets, showing a old three-story house made over for business,
adjoining a more recent seven-story loft building. Rephotographed
from an original made about
1898.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
